</td><td>约26,100人</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>星町水成</td><td>霍洛直播</td><td>约24,700人</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>甲贺流忍者！Pon Poko</td><td>独立的</td><td>约21,100人</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>葛叶</td><td>虹山寺</td><td>约21,000人</td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>大空昴</td><td>霍洛直播</td><td>约17,600人</td></tr><tr><td>十</td><td>高鲁・古拉<br>（高尔·古拉）</td><td>浩乐直播英语<br>(hololive-EN)</td><td>约16,700人</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">*根据流媒体图表</figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="cFk2JT18gz"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-may-reach-3-million-youtube-subscribers-during-the-year-end-and-new-year-holidays/">Hosho Marine提出年末年初频道订阅人数达到300万的可能性</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“年末年初，Hosho Marine 有可能达到 300 万订户” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-may-reach-3-million-youtube-subscribers-during-the-year-end-and-new-year-holidays/embed/#?secret=z4gz0xBeki#?secret=cFk2JT18gz" data-secret="cFk2JT18gz" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="vfmtz658299fd05266" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
